nodes.text: Good morning Dr. Person1,  Hope you are doing well. I had my prolia shot today with Dr. Person2. She went over my meds and said all ok for covid vaccine except was not sure about xarelto or Xeloda. She instructed me to check with you. Please let me know if the two meds will be ok and safe for me to get the vaccine. Thanks so much.
